description: Police are conducting a major bushland search operation in Glenory using specialist officers and cadaver dogs in connection with the disappearance of 85-year-old Chris Baghsarian, who has been missing for 10 days. A burnt-out car found in Westmead last week is believed to be connected to the abduction, and Baghsarian's family remains without information about his whereabouts while he has been without medication.
